### ✅ Fix #11c — `total_cost_analyzer`

Bug: `total_assignments = len(assignments)` as denominator was inflated.
Fixed to use `len(demand_assignments)`.

**R3 verification:** rate stays 100.00 EXCELLENT (this QA env has no
